23 (A) IN THIS SECTION, “STATE CORRECTIONAL FACILITY” HAS THE MEANING
24 STATED IN § 1–101 OF THE CORRECTIONAL SERVICES ARTICLE.
25 (B) ON A WEEKLY BASIS, THE DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY AND
26 CORRECTIONAL SERVICES SHALL ELECTRONICALLY TRANSMIT TO THE STATE
27 BOARD A LIST THAT INCLUDES THE NAME AND NEW RESIDENTIAL ADDRESS OF EACH
28 INDIVIDUAL WHO WAS RELEASED FROM INCARCERATION AT A STATE
29 CORRECTIONAL FACILITY IN THE PRECEDING WEEK.

